metadata.name: Red Sunrise
metadata.description:
The objective image of the future of humanity is formed by the collision of various images, meanings and their cultural transgression. Chronicles of future races is a kind of melting pot, in which both close and opposite things can mix, combine and interact, giving birth to renewed images of the future of our world. Oil on canvas, 115x140cm, 2018
